Package org.eclipse.wst.jsdt.chromium.debug.core.sourcemap

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    SourcePositionMap
    A map between "user" and "vm" source positions.
    SourcePositionMap.Token
    A token that can be kept and used later to check, whether source map has been updated.
    SourcePositionMapBuilder
    A builder for SourcePositionMap.
    SourcePositionMapBuilder.MappingHandle
    A handle that gives control over created mapping.
    TextSectionMapping
    Defines a mapping from one text file into another one.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    PositionMapBuilderImpl
    Implementation of SourcePositionMapBuilder and SourcePositionMap.
    SourcePosition
    Defines a position within a whole source base.
    SourcePositionMapBuilder.ResourceSection
    Defines a section of a source file, contains a resource id and start and end point in text.
    TextSectionMapping.TextPoint
    A structure of line/column.
    TextSectionMappingImpl
    A default implementation of TextSectionMapping.

    TextSectionMapping.Direction
